│              Blockchain Network                          │
│      (Ethereum, BSC, Polygon, Arbitrum)                 │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Project Structure

```
bancafi-wallet/
├── contracts/                           # Smart contracts
│   ├── BancafiSavingsAccount.sol       # Main savings contract
│   └── MockERC20.sol                   # Mock token for testing
├── backend/                             # Backend API
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── controllers/                # API controllers
│   │   ├── models/                     # Database models
│   │   ├── routes/                     # API routes
│   │   ├── config/                     # Configuration
│   │   ├── utils/                      # Utilities
│   │   └── index.js                    # Server entry point
│   └── package.json
├── scripts/                             # Deployment & management
│   ├── deploy.js                       # Deploy contract
│   ├── add-token.js                    # Add supported token
│   └── fund-contract.js                # Fund for interest payments
├── test/                                # Contract tests
│   └── BancafiSavingsAccount.test.js
├── docs/                                # Documentation
│   ├── TECHNICAL_DOCUMENTATION.md      # Full technical docs
│   └── USER_GUIDE.md                   # User guide
├── hardhat.config.js                    # Hardhat configuration
└── package.json
```

## How It Works

### For Users

1. **Deposit**: Send tokens to your savings account (min 10 tokens)
2. **Earn**: Interest accrues every second automatically
3. **Compound**: Interest is added to balance on any interaction
4. **Withdraw**: Take out funds anytime with no penalties

### Interest Rates

- **Base APY**: 4.5% for all accounts
- **Bonus APY**: +2.5% after 90 days (total 7%)
- **Compounding**: Automatic on deposits, withdrawals, or manual claim

### Example Returns

| Deposit | Duration | APY | Interest Earned |
|---------|----------|-----|-----------------|
| $1,000  | 1 year   | 4.5% → 7% | $57.38 |
| $5,000  | 6 months | 4.5% → 7% | $168.42 |
| $10,000 | 1 year   | 4.5% → 7% | $673.00 |

## Smart Contract Features

### Security
- ✅ Reentrancy protection (OpenZeppelin)
- ✅ Pausable for emergencies
- ✅ Owner-only admin functions
- ✅ SafeERC20 for token transfers
- ✅ Input validation and bounds checking

### Functionality
- ✅ Multi-token support
- ✅ Instant deposits
- ✅ Instant withdrawals (no lock-up)
- ✅ Automatic interest calculation
- ✅ Manual interest claiming
- ✅ Account information queries
- ✅ Global statistics tracking

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 18.x
- Hardhat
- PostgreSQL
- Redis

### Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Compile contracts
npx hardhat compile

# Run tests
npx hardhat test

# Deploy contracts
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network <network>

# Start backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Security Features

- Multi-signature wallets for large operations
- Time-locked withdrawals
- Rate limiting and circuit breakers
- Regular security audits
- Emergency pause functionality

